 They have no error bars, right?

21:38.960 --> 21:41.040
 I got to think about other people's decisions around me.

21:41.040 --> 21:45.560
 I got to think about a collection of my decisions, even just thinking about like a medical treatment.

21:45.560 --> 21:50.400
